## Milestone 3 — Minimal Map & Navigation UI (Week 2)

**Goal:** World Map screen with a simple node graph for one region, using real data.

### Tasks
- [ ] Implement `screens/WorldMapScreen.tsx` layout per UI spec:
  - [ ] Top nav with current level, EXP, gold.
  - [ ] Region title and chapter selector.
  - [ ] SVG or canvas-based node map using `RegionNode` component.
- [ ] Implement `<RegionNode />` component:
