  - [ ] Buttons: [Fight (Auto)], [Idle Farm Here], [Boss Info].
- [ ] Implement basic route structure in `App.tsx`:
  - [ ] `/map` → WorldMapScreen
  - [ ] `/battle` → BattleScreen (placeholder)
