## Milestone 6 — Runes & Skill Slots (Week 4)

**Goal:** 4 active skill slots with link runes, using weapon compatibility rules.

### Tasks
- [ ] Implement `engine/runes/runeValidator.ts`:
  - [ ] Check weapon family restriction.
  - [ ] Enforce maxSupportLinks.
- [ ] Implement `engine/runes/skillLinkResolver.ts`:
  - [ ] Merge skill rune + link runes into effective DamagePacket modifiers.
- [ ] Implement `screens/RuneScreen.tsx` per UI spec:
  - [ ] 4 slots with skill + link sub-slots.
  - [ ] Rune inventory list.
  - [ ] Drag-to-equip or click-to-assign UX.
- [ ] Implement `<RuneCard />` component.
- [ ] Implement `hooks/useRuneEquip.ts`:
  - [ ] Equip skill runes to slots.
  - [ ] Equip link runes to sub-slots.
  - [ ] Update `useRuneStore` state.
- [ ] Hook combat pipeline to rune configuration:
  - [ ] `useCombatLoop` fetches skill for each slot and passes rune modifiers into DamagePacket when firing skills.
- [ ] Add minimal active skill selection UI in BattleScreen (1–4 slots, with cooldown display).

### Exit criteria
- [ ] Player can choose between at least 2 skill runes and 2 link runes.
- [ ] Battle uses chosen skill rune + link runes instead of hard-coded damage.
- [ ] Weapon-exclusive rune shows warning if incompatible, and cannot be equipped.

