## Milestone 8 — Shrine, Death & Respawn Flow (Week 5)

**Goal:** Fully functional death → shrine → back to map/battle flow.

### Tasks
- [ ] Implement `screens/ShrineScreen.tsx` modal per UI spec.
- [ ] On `PLAYER_DIED` event from BattleScene:
  - [ ] Open ShrineScreen modal.
  - [ ] Reset HP, barrier, resources in `usePlayerStore`.
  - [ ] Set current node to nearest shrine in `useMapStore`.
- [ ] Allow manual shrine visit from map node (Shrine type).
- [ ] Implement fast travel list from `useMapStore` discovered shrines.
- [ ] Ensure no XP/loot is granted on death.

### Exit criteria
- [ ] Dying in battle never hard-crashes; ShrineScreen always appears.
- [ ] Clicking [Return to Map] takes you back to `/map` with shrine selected.
- [ ] Fast travel between shrines works for already discovered shrines.

