## Milestone 9 — Offline Progression & Idle Summary (Week 6)

**Goal:** Idle farming + offline accrual with Offline Summary screen.

### Tasks
- [ ] Implement `engine/progression/offlineAccrual.ts` following spec:
  - [ ] Use lastOnlineTimestamp, currentRegionId, player level, region offlineRateMultiplier.
  - [ ] Cap at MAX_OFFLINE_SECONDS.
- [ ] Implement `hooks/useOfflineAccrual.ts`:
  - [ ] On app load, read saved state.
  - [ ] Calculate offline gains; store in `useOfflineStore`.
  - [ ] Show OfflineSummaryScreen modal if gains > 0.
- [ ] Implement `screens/OfflineSummaryScreen.tsx` per UI spec.
- [ ] On [Collect & Continue], apply EXP + materials to `usePlayerStore` and `useInventoryStore`.
- [ ] Enforce rule: no rare runes / uniques in offline accrual.
- [ ] Save idle farming node when player presses [Idle Farm Here] on map.

### Exit criteria
- [ ] Closing the game for a few minutes and reopening shows Offline Summary.
- [ ] EXP and materials from offline accrual are correctly applied.
- [ ] Player can set/change idle farming node from World Map.

