## Milestone 10 — Boss Detail & Boss Battle (Week 6–7)

**Goal:** Dedicated boss encounters with telegraphs, multi-phase behavior, and a Boss Detail page.

### Tasks
- [ ] Implement `screens/BossDetailScreen.tsx` using UI spec:
  - [ ] Boss stats, phases, abilities, recommended power.
  - [ ] Full loot table (signature + shared drops) with rates.
  - [ ] Personal kill count and observed drops.
- [ ] Implement `phaser/scenes/BossScene.ts`:
  - [ ] Use boss sprite and HP bar at top.
  - [ ] Implement telegraph attacks (warning overlay + delay).
  - [ ] Implement phase transitions using HP thresholds from `bosses.json`.
- [ ] Wire [Fight (Manual)] button to `/battle?bossId=...` using BossScene.
- [ ] Hook up boss-specific drop table in `dropResolver.ts` with signature runes/uniques.
- [ ] Update ResultScreen to show special highlight when signature rune drops.

### Exit criteria
- [ ] You can open Boss Detail from the boss node on map.
- [ ] Boss fight uses real telegraphs and phases.
- [ ] Boss kill rewards match loot table probabilities.

