## Milestone 11 — Chapter 1 Story & Polishing (Week 7–8)

**Goal:** Tie everything together into a coherent Chapter 1 experience.

### Tasks
- [ ] Define `chapters.json` with at least Chapter 1:
  - [ ] Title, list of region IDs, chapter boss ID, unlock conditions.
  - [ ] A few `ChapterDialogue` entries for intro + boss kill.
- [ ] Implement `screens/StoryScreen.tsx` to show dialogue scenes:
  - [ ] Speaker portrait, name, text lines.
  - [ ] Advance on click or tap.
- [ ] Trigger story sequences at:
  - [ ] Chapter 1 start (first time enter Edo Streets).
  - [ ] First time boss_oni_general killed.
- [ ] Polish UI elements:
  - [ ] Apply color and typography tokens (near-PoE style) across screens.
  - [ ] Add basic SFX (attack, hit, death, drop) via Phaser.
- [ ] Add Settings panel (BGM/SFX volume, auto-farm toggle, battle speed).
- [ ] Fix any UX blockers discovered during playtests.

### Exit criteria
- [ ] A fresh profile can:
  - [ ] Start game → see intro story.
  - [ ] Farm Market Camp → gain EXP, loot, and level up.
  - [ ] Equip new gear and adjust runes.
  - [ ] Allocate passive points.
  - [ ] Die and respawn at shrine.
  - [ ] Set idle farming and collect offline gains.
  - [ ] See Boss Detail, fight and defeat boss, see outro story.
- [ ] Chapter 1 can be fully completed end-to-end.

