### Tasks
- [ ] Add error handling and fallback for missing JSON data.
- [ ] Add simple analytics logging (e.g. console or localStats) for:
  - [ ] Time to first kill, time to first boss kill.
  - [ ] Average TTK on Market Camp and boss.
  - [ ] Most-used skill runes.
- [ ] Add in-game debug panel (toggle by key) to show:
  - [ ] Current DPS estimate.
  - [ ] Current TTK vs target ranges.
  - [ ] Current additive and multiplicative buckets.
- [ ] Profile performance on mobile browser (FPS during BattleScene).
- [ ] Tag issues in GitHub with labels: `combat`, `UI`, `data`, `performance`, `polish`.

